      <description>To turn on auto sync on Google, go to your Google Account settings and enable the &amp;lsquo;Sync&amp;rsquo; option, allowing your data to be synchronized across all devices. This feature ensures that your Google account data, including contacts, calendar, and browser history, remains up-to-date and accessible from any device.</description>
